<item><title>Daily Briefing — Monday, March 30, 2026</title><description>Morning daily briefing covering weather, calendar, messages, and today's top stories.

00:00:00 Opening &amp; Day Overview
00:01:30 Your Calendar &amp; Messages
00:04:00 Local News &amp; Quick Status
00:05:30 Iran War &amp; Defense
00:08:00 Anthropic &amp; Pentagon Case
00:09:00 SpaceX IPO
00:10:30 Tech &amp; AI News
00:13:00 Jobs &amp; Sports
00:14:30 Closing</description><content:encoded>&lt;h2&gt;Monday, March 30, 2026 — Daily Briefing&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;Local News&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The DHS shutdown reaches day 45, but TSA workers are getting paychecks starting today thanks to a Trump presidential memorandum redirecting funds. &lt;a href="https://www.cnbc.com/2026/03/27/tsa-dhs-paychecks-shutdown.html"&gt;TSA Paychecks Continue →&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;Iran &amp; Defense&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Iran war enters day 31 with 50,000 US troops in the Middle East. Trump tells the Financial Times he might "take the oil" and seize Kharg Island. The Wall Street Journal reports consideration of a military operation to seize uranium enrichment material. &lt;a href="https://www.washingtonpost.com/national-security/2026/03/28/trump-iran-ground-troops-marines/"&gt;US Ground Operations →&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2026/3/29/pentagon-readies-for-weeks-of-us-ground-operations-in-iran-report"&gt;Pentagon Readiness →&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;Anthropic &amp; Government&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Judge Lin's injunction against Pentagon interference with Anthropic holds. Government has until Thursday to appeal to the Ninth Circuit. All three Anthropic watchlist roles remain open: Institute Analyst, Communications Manager, and Geopolitics Analyst.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;SpaceX IPO&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;SpaceX is preparing the largest IPO in history: $75 billion at a $1.75 trillion valuation. That's more than the entire US IPO market raised in 2024 and 2025 combined. Polymarket gives it an 89.5% chance of being the biggest IPO of the year. Musk recently merged XAI into SpaceX; all eleven XAI co-founders have left.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;Tech &amp; AI News&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Anthropic's Claude Mythos leak continues. Axios reports the company is privately warning government officials that the model "presages an upcoming wave of models that can exploit vulnerabilities in ways that far outpace the efforts of defenders." &lt;a href="https://fortune.com/2026/03/26/anthropic-says-testing-mythos-powerful-new-ai-model-after-data-leak-reveals-its-existence-step-change-in-capabilities/"&gt;Claude Mythos Leak →&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.cnbc.com/2026/03/26/anthropic-pentagon-dod-claude-court-ruling.html"&gt;Pentagon DOD Claude Court Ruling →&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The FTC chairman called media companies demanding payment for AI training data "rent-seeking" and "collecting tolls" — effectively giving AI companies a green light to train on news content.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NASA's Artemis crew entered quarantine ahead of a potential Wednesday launch. This would be the first crewed trip around the moon since 1972.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;Your Day&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ben arrives today to help with carpet installation (scheduled for tomorrow at 9 AM). Payday is also tomorrow. Wednesday: Apple's 50th anniversary, Q2 starts, and Karen announces her retirement at 11 AM. Thursday is loaded: Anthropic pilot discussion at 9 AM, Bill Review Training at 2 PM, dinner with Alex, Chris, and Dustin at 6 PM, and the government appeal deadline coincides with your own workplace pilot meeting.&lt;/p&gt;</content:encoded><enclosure url="https://jacobbrooke95.github.io/daily-briefing-podcast/episodes/daily-briefing-2026-03-30-audio.mp3" length="2693232" type="audio/mpeg" /><itunes:image href="https://jacobbrooke95.github.io/daily-briefing-podcast/episode-art-2026-03-30.jpg" /><podcast:transcript url="https://jacobbrooke95.github.io/daily-briefing-podcast/transcripts/transcript-2026-03-30.vtt" type="text/vtt" language="en" /><guid isPermaLink="false">briefing-2026-03-30</guid><pubDate>Mon, 30 Mar 2026 06:13:01 -0500</pubDate><itunes:duration>7:28</itunes:duration><itunes:episode>13</itunes:episode><itunes:episodeType>full</itunes:episodeType></item>
