<item>
      <title>Deep Dive — Claude Mythos: Anthropic's Biggest Leak and IPO Plans</title>
      <description>A deep dive into the Claude Mythos leak — Anthropic's new Capybara-tier model with unprecedented cybersecurity capabilities, the Wall Street selloff it triggered, and the October 2026 IPO plans revealed the same day.</description>
      <content:encoded>&lt;h2&gt;The Leak&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;On March 26, 2026, a CMS misconfiguration at Anthropic exposed roughly 3,000 unpublished blog assets — including a draft post describing Claude Mythos, a new model tier above Opus. Security researchers Roy Paz (LayerX) and Alexandre Pauwels (Cambridge) found the exposed data store. Fortune broke the story.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;What Is Capybara?&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Capybara is Anthropic's new fourth model tier, positioned above Opus. Claude Mythos is the first model in this tier. Anthropic calls it "a step change" and "the most capable we've built to date," with dramatically higher scores in coding, reasoning, and cybersecurity.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Cybersecurity Concerns&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;The draft warns Mythos is "far ahead of any other AI model in cyber capabilities" — able to find and exploit software vulnerabilities at machine speed. This triggered a major cybersecurity stock selloff: CrowdStrike -7%, Palo Alto Networks -6%, Tenable -11%, Zscaler -4.5%.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;IPO Plans&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Bloomberg reported the same day that Anthropic is targeting an October 2026 IPO, potentially raising 0B+. The company is valued at ~80B after a 0B February funding round, running at 4B annualized revenue. The timing has fueled skepticism about whether the leak was truly accidental.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Open Questions&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;When will Mythos be available via API? What will pricing look like? Will cybersecurity concerns trigger regulation? And was this leak intentional pre-IPO marketing?&lt;/p&gt;</content:encoded>
      <enclosure url="https://jacobbrooke95.github.io/daily-briefing-podcast/episodes/mythos-deep-dive-2026-03-28.mp3" length="1504800" type="audio/mpeg" />
      <itunes:image href="https://jacobbrooke95.github.io/daily-briefing-podcast/episode-art-mythos-2026-03-28.jpg" />
      <guid isPermaLink="false">custom-2026-03-28-mythos-deep-dive</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 28 Mar 2026 09:45:00 -0500</pubDate>
      <itunes:duration>4:00</itunes:duration>
      <itunes:episode>5</itunes:episode>
